==Definition==
"Woo-Woo" or sometimes just, "Woo" is a derogatory label used by many in the [[skeptic]] community against [[paranormal]], [[occult]], or [[pseudoscientific]] phenomena.
==Origin==
It has been suggested that "Woo Woo" is intended to imitate the eerie background music of [[sci-fi ]]/[[horror films]] and [[TV shows]].
